data.description:
House is available to rent by the October 1, 2020. Single floor ranch house, 10 minute drive to the main Van Deman gate, almost never any traffic, 5 piece master bath, large walk in shareable master closet, master bedroom suite is completely seperate from the other bedrooms making it ideal for a live-in mother in law, 2.5 attached car garage with storage crawlspace, garage walk in through laundry room. Oversized kitchen and pantry, gorgeous flowery front and back yard lots of mature rose bushes shrubs and trees. Pets are allowed, no more than three large (100lbs each) pets. Any damage to house will be taken from deposit.

Renter pays for all utilities. See contact for all terms.
data.whatILove: The layout of this house is amazing, lots of privacy between the bedrooms, open living room concept.
